<div class="title">Helped Chills and Sweats</div>
<div class="substance">Clonidine & Diazepam</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Contourcrown&Exact=1">Contourcrown</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Contourcrown. "Helped Chills and Sweats: An Experience with Clonidine & Diazepam (exp53287)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 14, 2006. erowid.org/exp/53287</div>

<br/>



